track_notes:
From/to Pen Y Pass
UP:   Miners Track
DOWN: Pyg Track
Long walk, you could include Y Lliwedd en-route. Can be slippery on ascent to Yr Aran in wet conditions. Care must be taken on path descending Snowdon, very loose rock and steep.
track_title: Snowdon via Watkin path and Yr Aran

track_notes: Straightforward route from Rhyd Ddu WHR station. One of the quieter paths.
